Documentation of the installation of the video piece "Stone Canoe" at the exhibition "Guess Ready Review" at the Kolman & Pryor Gallery in Minneapolis - April, 2014
Filmed on the 2013 Eco Artists Workshop on Mallard Island, Rainy Lake, MN. Organized by Kate Casanova.
